---
import MarketingLayout from "../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/marketing/Footer.astro";
---

<MarketingLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="BrandKlip Privacy Policy and data handling commitments."
  canonicalPath="/privacypolicy"
>
  <section class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pt-32 pb-24" data-reveal>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-8 text-[var(--brand-black)]">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none prose-headings:font-semibold prose-a:text-green-600 hover:prose-a:text-green-500">
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--ink-50)] mb-8 font-mono tracking-wider uppercase">Last Updated: March 2025</p>

      <h2>1. INTRODUCTION</h2>
      <p>
        BrandKlip ("we," "us," "our," or "Platform") is committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring transparency about how we collect, use, and protect your personal data.
      </p>
      <p>This Privacy Policy explains our data practices in full compliance with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Information Technology Act, 2000</li>
        <li>Information Technology Rules, 2011</li>
        <li>Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023 (DPDP Act)</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Current Status:</strong> Operated as sole proprietorship</p>
      <p><strong>Future:</strong> Will transition to company after PMF validation</p>

      <h2>2. PERSONAL DATA WE COLLECT</h2>
      <h3>2.1 Information You Provide Directly</h3>
      <p><strong>For All Users (Creators &amp; Brands):</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Full name</li>
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>Phone number</li>
        <li>Password (stored as hashed, never plain text)</li>
        <li>Profile picture (optional)</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>For Creators:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Instagram handle</li>
        <li>Follower count (self-reported)</li>
        <li>Content niches/categories</li>
        <li>Video submission links (Google Drive)</li>
        <li>Order proof screenshots (product purchase verification)</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>For Brands:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Company name</li>
        <li>Business category</li>
        <li>Website URL (optional)</li>
        <li>Brand logo (optional)</li>
        <li>Campaign briefs and descriptions</li>
        <li>Product links</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>2.2 Information Automatically Collected</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
        <li>Clicks and interactions on Platform</li>
        <li>Search queries</li>
        <li>Campaign browsing history</li>
        <li>Video submission timestamps</li>
        <li>Device type and operating system</li>
        <li>Approximate location (via IP, not precise)</li>
        <li>Browser type and version</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>2.3 Cookies &amp; Tracking</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Session cookies (required for login)</li>
        <li>Authentication tokens (for security)</li>
        <li>Analytics cookies (optional, privacy-respecting)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>2.4 What We Do NOT Collect</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Actual bank account numbers</li>
        <li>UPI IDs</li>
        <li>Credit card details</li>
        <li>Biometric data</li>
        <li>Health information</li>
        <li>Government ID numbers (except as required by payment processor)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. HOW WE USE YOUR PERSONAL DATA</h2>
      <p>We use your data to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Create and manage your account</li>
        <li>Process Creator applications</li>
        <li>Facilitate video submissions and approvals</li>
        <li>Process payments via Razorpay</li>
        <li>Send transactional emails and WhatsApp notifications</li>
        <li>Platform improvement &amp; analytics</li>
        <li>Maintain platform security and integrity</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. WHO WE SHARE YOUR DATA WITH</h2>
      <p>We share data with verified third-party service providers only when necessary:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Razorpay:</strong> For payment processing</li>
        <li><strong>Brevo:</strong> For email communications</li>
        <li><strong>Google Cloud:</strong> For secure data hosting</li>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> For anonymized usage insights</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do NOT sell or rent your personal data to marketers or researchers.</p>

      <h2>5. YOUR RIGHTS</h2>
      <p>Under the DPDP Act 2023, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Correct inaccurate or incomplete information</li>
        <li>Request erasure of your data ("Right to be Forgotten")</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for processing</li>
        <li>Data portability</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>6. CONTACT INFORMATION</h2>
      <p>For any privacy-related inquiries, please contact us at:</p>
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> hello@brandklip.com</p>
      <p><strong>Grievance Officer:</strong> Divyank</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</MarketingLayout>
